{"tid":288057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍: 珍惜生命 遠離毒品","createTime":"2017-06-18T02:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T21:47:10.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4416ff523042a2dbc11ae352b7cc7b3d8ed41d10","tid":288057,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/101018_78c7783ed833a02576497f644a788dc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F101018_78c7783ed833a02576497f644a788dc6.jpg&h=8609a5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騰訊娛樂訊 近日，成龍領銜演員倪新宇、郭峰、紀敏佳、蔡國慶、周筆暢、汪正正等眾星共同錄製禁毒公益歌曲《生命》。<br />\n該歌曲為著名音樂人郭峰激情創作，主題鮮明、旋律優美，有很強的衝擊力和感染力。現場錄製中，郭峰對倪新宇的唱功給予了肯定。<br />\n參與錄製的明星共同在展板上簽字承諾「珍愛生命，遠離毒品」，並接過由國家禁毒辦頒發的榮譽證書。在後台接受媒體採訪時倪新宇說：「非常榮幸能來參加此次的公益歌曲錄製，大家一定要遠離毒品，珍惜生命。」並表示：最近也在參與禁毒宣傳的一些公益活動，將會繼續的支持宣傳下去。"},{"pid":"440a146a17763f2bbc58aded1f54491ca55d4d83","tid":288057,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"祝你馬到功成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6833243567a2b6c7647ae6bcdbe2b5e1bfd2976a","tid":288057,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32512ded98471d46de8ffc855dba8745cd9a9ac8","tid":288057,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"立馬珍惜生命，遠離鴉片"},{"pid":"349a73dd9d94eae0d83626c6c2a6ab14e1e54c9e","tid":288057,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f654343a443c39738ed4d39f3e02fc5cac73a345","tid":288057,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b87f58dc372cbb13d9cad1ff6fae38e219a20ea","tid":288057,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T